In the debug build (with _DEBUG defined) the code assigns da->ready_for_hashing = false immediately before calling mhd_assert(0), which is intended to abort/terminate on failure. Because the assertion will stop execution, the assignment is executed but has no observable effect on program behaviour; removing it would not change behaviour (the assertion still aborts). Thus this assignment is dead code.
